444b77082d44d5c710d19d752dfd885442cc85c5f1bf3eda2280baed8b0937b1e2175433db93b3b6ce741f94fd71cf8f5ed265852813a0b446bebff51f8c5fc1  0001-Cargo.lock-Bump-the-newsblur-API-crate.patch
